title: Positive Grid BIAS Pro v1.1.0.3.7.4.Incl.Patch.and.Keygen.rar
description:
Positive Grid BIAS Professional 
1.Install the product.
2.Load this plugin in your DAW and it will create a  folder: 
C:Users(User name)DocumentsBias  And then close the plugin.
3.Replace .dll files with the Cracked .dll files.
4.Run the KeyGen.exe, a file will be created.
Copy file into this path: C:Users(User name)DocumentsBias
5.Run the plugin.Login your Positive Grid account,you can download and share
new amp models on the  Tone Cloud.
6.Enjoy!

NOTE:Only VST format has been Cracked.
